            Blackstone Targets $10 Billion for Asia Fund
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image
          padding="10px 12px"
          width="600px"
          src="https://www.altdaily.co/email/images/an-oct-4-1.jpg"
          alt="Blackstone Targets $10 Billion for Asia Fund"
