              target="_blank"
              >over 40</a
            >
            hedge funds with more than $1 billion in assets under management
            each, employing more than 1,000 people. This rapid growth is part of
            a wider expansion in Dubai’s financial sector, where employee
            numbers have surged by two-thirds since 2019. With Dubai offering a
            favorable business environment, financial professionals are flocking
            to the city. The hedge fund boom is expected to continue, with firms
            like Capricorn Fund Managers launching platforms to make it even
            easier for hedge funds to set up shop in Dubai.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
